score[p] =
    (2.0 * days_since_last_solved) +
    (1.5 * difficulty of the question);

    days_since_last_solved: Number of days since the user last solved a problem in this topic.
    confidence[p]: User's confidence level for problem p (1 to 5).
                    this should not be self reported
                    I'll rather take this from the users performance in the coderoom

    difficulty[p]: Difficulty rating of problem p (1 to 10).